trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel" />.
The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition> to set the position of a child control in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control.
